        639,
        847
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In certain scenarios, you might want to provision a customized cluster.",
      "pos": [
        848,
        919
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For example, you might want to attach an external metadata store to keep your Hive metadata persistent beyond the lifetime of a cluster, or you might want to use additional storage with the cluster.",
      "pos": [
        920,
        1118
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For such and other scenarios, this article provides instructions on how to use the Azure portal, Azure PowerShell, or the HDInsight .NET SDK to provision a customized Spark cluster on HDInsight.",
