        1339,
        1426
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "See <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Get Azure free trial<ept id=\"p1\">](http://azure.microsoft.com/documentation/videos/get-azure-free-trial-for-testing-hadoop-in-hdinsight/)</ept>.",
